T1  - Strategy, Structure, the Environment, and Financial Performance in 48 United Kingdom Companies
AU  - Grinyer, Peter H.
AU  - Yasai-Ardekani, Masound
AU  - Al-Bazzaz, Shawki
Y1  - 1980/06/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/255427
